- Apa?

281
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:45,700
Aku belajar dan terus belajar.

282
00:18:46,370 --> 00:18:47,670
Lalu bekerja.

283
00:18:52,210 --> 00:18:54,509
Ini kali pertamaku melakukan hal seperti ini.

284
00:18:55,339 --> 00:18:56,910
Walaupun kamu tidak akan memercayainya.

285
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:02,049
Kenapa kamu hidup seperti itu?

286
00:19:04,650 --> 00:19:05,819
Ya...

287
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,089
Sebagian karena kepribadianku.

288
00:19:09,589 --> 00:19:12,460
Ibu membesarkan kami bertiga sendirian,

289
00:19:13,089 --> 00:19:15,829
jadi, aku harus dapat beasiswa.

290
00:19:19,229 --> 00:19:20,670
Aku masih merasa

291
00:19:21,130 --> 00:19:23,670
keluargamu amat menyayangimu.

292
00:19:23,739 --> 00:19:24,999
Menurutmu begitu?

293
00:19:26,970 --> 00:19:27,970
Bagus.

294
00:19:28,039 --> 00:19:30,180
Ibu akan senang mendengar itu.

295
00:19:33,950 --> 00:19:34,979
Bolehkah aku

296
00:19:35,309 --> 00:19:37,579
pergi makan sup tulang sapi lagi?

297
00:19:40,819 --> 00:19:41,890
Apa?

298
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:44,960
Kenapa tidak? Kamu pernah mengajakku sekali.

299
00:19:47,890 --> 00:19:51,759
Itu... Itu

300
00:19:51,829 --> 00:19:53,370
hanya sebagai anak buahku.

301
00:19:54,100 --> 00:19:55,769
Kamu tiba-tiba malu.

302
00:19:56,239 --> 00:19:59,009
Kuharap anggota tim yang lain bisa melihatmu sekarang.

303
00:19:59,670 --> 00:20:01,910
Sayang sekali hanya aku yang bisa melihatnya.

304
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:03,509
Kenapa kamu begitu?

305
00:20:06,049 --> 00:20:07,450
Kamu amat cantik.

306
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:08,650
Benar?

307
00:20:09,220 --> 00:20:10,380
Kamu mengakuinya?

308
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,019
Hentikan.

309
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:13,190
Aku mengakuinya.

310
00:20:21,430 --> 00:20:23,430
Ada apa? Apa? Siapa?

311
00:20:24,729 --> 00:20:25,799
Siapa?

312
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:33,809
Kamu mau ke tempatku untuk melihat kucingku?

313
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:39,380
Kucingmu? Kita belum sampai sana.

314
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:43,350
Kenapa belum? Kenapa?

315
00:20:44,049 --> 00:20:45,789
Kamu selalu bisa mampir.

316
00:20:47,819 --> 00:20:48,920
Buka mulutmu.

317
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,339
Halo, Pak Park.

318
00:21:09,309 --> 00:21:10,539
Hai, Min Hye.

319
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,650
Bagaimana ini?

320
00:21:20,049 --> 00:21:22,220
Tae Ju, kumohon.

321
00:21:23,890 --> 00:21:24,989
Tolong rahasiakan ini.

322
00:21:25,059 --> 00:21:27,130
Pak Park, kenapa berlutut?

323
00:21:27,190 --> 00:21:28,259
Tamat riwayatku

324
00:21:28,329 --> 00:21:29,930
jika Bu Kang tahu aku mengencani pegawai kantor.

325
00:21:29,999 --> 00:21:31,430
Tolong rahasiakan ini, ya?

326
00:21:32,329 --> 00:21:34,829
Tae Ju, masalahnya...

327
00:21:35,569 --> 00:21:38,569
Mi Hye, kembalilah ke sana. Akan kuurus ini.

328
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:47,210
Akan kurahasiakan. Jangan cemas.

329
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:53,220
Terima kasih, Tae Ju. Terima kasih banyak.

330
00:21:53,890 --> 00:21:54,920
Omong-omong,

331
00:21:56,489 --> 00:21:59,390
kenapa kamu bilang Bu Kang tidak boleh tahu soal ini?

332
00:22:00,390 --> 00:22:02,229
Bu Kang belum pernah berkencan.

333
00:22:02,289 --> 00:22:03,700
- Apa?
- Sial.

334
00:22:03,759 --> 00:22:04,829
Dia belum pernah berkencan?

335
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:05,900
Ya.

336
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:08,200
Menurutmu kenapa

337
00:22:08,269 --> 00:22:10,239
dia bekerja sepanjang tahun?

338
00:22:10,299 --> 00:22:12,239
Itu karena dia tidak punya perasaan.

339
00:22:12,299 --> 00:22:14,339
Terutama cinta.

340
00:22:14,410 --> 00:22:17,539
Dia tidak punya cinta di hatinya sama sekali.

341
00:22:17,910 --> 00:22:20,680
Aku sudah lama bekerja dengan Bu Kang,

342
00:22:20,950 --> 00:22:23,479
tapi hanya pernah melihatnya bersama para eksekutif.

343
00:22:23,979 --> 00:22:25,650
Yang dia pedulikan hanyalah pekerjaan.

344
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,450
Kamu kira dia akan mengizinkanku mengencani seseorang di kantor?

345
00:22:27,519 --> 00:22:29,289
Dia mungkin menyuruhku bunuh diri.

346
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:32,759
Begitu rupanya.

347
00:22:32,829 --> 00:22:35,630
Bu Kang belum pernah berkencan.

348
00:22:37,329 --> 00:22:39,569
Omong-omong, kamu kemari bersama pacarmu?

349
00:22:40,370 --> 00:22:42,269
Ya. Aku bersama pacarku.

350
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,600
Boleh kusapa dia?

351
00:22:44,769 --> 00:22:47,170
Tidak. Mungkin lain kali.

352
00:22:48,910 --> 00:22:52,410
Baik, bagaimanapun, terima kasih.

353
00:22:53,309 --> 00:22:54,350
Tolong rahasiakan ini.

354
00:22:55,210 --> 00:22:56,279
Baik.

355
00:22:57,779 --> 00:23:01,289
Min Hye, jangan cemas. Aku sudah mengurusnya.

356
00:23:14,029 --> 00:23:16,140
Kita tidak punya pilihan. Kita harus tetap di sini

357
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,739
sampai Pak Park pergi.

358
00:23:17,870 --> 00:23:20,269
Pak Park sialan!

359
00:23:21,039 --> 00:23:22,509
Jadi, kamu belum pernah berkencan?

360
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:27,850
Sudah kubilang. Aku hanya belajar dan bekerja.

361
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:31,579
Bagaimanapun, buat Pak Park pulang.

362
00:23:31,650 --> 00:23:33,850
Kita tidak bisa tetap di tenda seperti ini sepanjang waktu.

363
00:23:35,049 --> 00:23:36,819
- Lantas, ayo keluar.
- Tidak!

364
00:23:36,890 --> 00:23:38,360
Kenapa tidak? Aku tidak masalah.

365
00:23:39,529 --> 00:23:42,329
Karena kini aku tahu rahasia Pak Park,

366
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:45,200
bukankah kita harus memberitahunya rahasia kita?

367
00:23:45,930 --> 00:23:48,130
Bahwa kamu pacarku?

368
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,069
Bahwa kita berkencan.

369
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:51,499
Kamu sudah gila?

370
00:23:52,539 --> 00:23:53,710
Kamu tidak akan melakukan sesuatu?

371
00:23:54,610 --> 00:23:55,610
Ya...

372
00:23:58,640 --> 00:23:59,680
Lupakan.

373
00:24:02,009 --> 00:24:03,249
Baiklah kalau begitu.

374
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:05,350
- Pak Park.
- Tunggu.

375
00:24:13,229 --> 00:24:14,289
Cepat.

376
00:24:27,339 --> 00:24:28,739
- Itu Pak Park.
- Astaga.

377
00:24:28,809 --> 00:24:29,979
Aku bercanda.

378
00:25:58,130 --> 00:26:00,299
Pastikan memakaikannya secara merata.

379
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:02,670
Uban sungguh mengganggu ibu.

380
00:26:02,739 --> 00:26:04,670
Aku bisa.

381
00:26:04,739 --> 00:26:05,870
Jangan cemas.

382
00:26:06,410 --> 00:26:09,509
Ibu seharusnya meminta Mi Hye melakukan ini.

383
00:26:09,579 --> 00:26:11,110
Ibu tidak akan membiarkan Mi Hye mengecat rambut ibu.

384
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:13,110
Dia akan membuat leher ibu terkena cat.

385
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:16,519
Apa menurut Ibu,

386
00:26:16,579 --> 00:26:19,489
toko buku tempatnya bekerja bagus?

387
00:26:19,890 --> 00:26:21,789
Tentu saja.

388
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:25,160
Ayah pemiliknya pernah menerbitkan buku Mi Hye.

389
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:26,489
Sungguh?

390
00:26:27,089 --> 00:26:30,160
Jika putra Pak Kim, dia pasti tampan.

391
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,329
Kurasa itulah alasan Jae Bum mabuk.

392
00:26:33,999 --> 00:26:35,029
Astaga.

393
00:26:36,269 --> 00:26:38,069
Jae Bum masih tidur?

394
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:39,910
Dia baru saja pergi.

395
00:26:40,170 --> 00:26:41,470
Lepaskan aku.

396
00:26:41,670 --> 00:26:43,539
Astaga, hentikan.

397
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,779
Tunggu.

398
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:46,549
Pak Bang, jangan melemparnya.

399
00:26:49,850 --> 00:26:51,079
Pak Bang!

400
00:26:52,850 --> 00:26:55,549
Hentikan. Jangan dilempar.

401
00:26:58,620 --> 00:26:59,789
Pak Bang.

402
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:10,999
Pak Bang!

403
00:27:16,779 --> 00:27:17,880
Pak Bang!

404
00:27:18,809 --> 00:27:21,650
Pak Bang, tolong tenang.

405
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:24,319
Tolong tenang sedikit.

406
00:27:24,579 --> 00:27:27,650
Katakan di mana Mi Hye. Sekarang juga!

407
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:30,259
Aku tidak tahu. Sungguh tidak tahu.

408
00:27:31,059 --> 00:27:34,130
Bukan seperti itu. Itu bukan liburan

409
00:27:34,190 --> 00:27:35,789
seperti yang kamu bayangkan.

410
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:37,829
Itu murni rapat perencanaan.

411
00:27:37,900 --> 00:27:39,870
Rapat perencanaan apanya?

412
00:27:39,930 --> 00:27:41,769
Murni? Itu konyol.

413
00:27:41,829 --> 00:27:43,239
Pria dan wanita pergi berlibur bersama.

414
00:27:43,299 --> 00:27:45,600
Bagaimana bisa murni?

415
00:27:45,670 --> 00:27:48,610
Katakan saja di mana Mi Hye!

416
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:49,779
"'Nyaris, Malam yang Luar Biasa'"

417
00:27:53,479 --> 00:27:54,680
Sungguh menyenangkan?

418
00:27:56,319 --> 00:27:58,049
